      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or as a major restoration project. Mechanically, the engine suffers from significant oil leaks and a persistent misfire, while the transmission exhibits heavy slipping in higher gears. The exterior shows extensive rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with several deep dents and faded paint. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the air conditioning is currently non-functional. Prospective buyers should expect to invest substantial time and money into repairs to make this vehicle roadworthy again.",
