    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and it's honestly been such a reliable companion. It's in great shape and has been well-cared for over the years. It drives smoothly and still looks wonderful parked in the driveway! Perfect for someone who wants a solid, dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. Feel free to reach out if you have questions or want to come by for a test drive\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
