    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2008 Chevrolet Corvette Z06, a pinnacle of American engineering featuring the naturally aspirated 7.0L LS7 V8. This powerhouse utilizes a dry-sump lubrication system, titanium connecting rods, and CNC-ported cylinder heads to deliver a linear power band and a 7,000 RPM redline. The hydroformed aluminum chassis remains rigid, paired with a rear-mounted Tremec TR-6060 six-speed manual transaxle for optimal weight distribution. This specimen has undergone a critical 'heads-fix' to address factory valve guide tolerances, ensuring long-term valvetrain reliability. The suspension geometry is dialed in, and the factory-spec Brembo braking system provides consistent thermal management. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including oil pressure and coolant temps\u2014remain within ideal operating parameters. A purist\u2019s machine with documented maintenance of its high-performance consumables.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well. Clean title.",
