    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scuff on the passenger side mirror\u2014honest wear from a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the upholstery is clean and free of tears, and every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, and I have kept a complete folder of maintenance receipts. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner, offering a premium driving experience and the peace of mind that comes with a documented service history.",
